Package frogger.model.actor

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Transformable
    A class implements the Transformable interface to implements Transformable.transform(long now) transform the state of the actor.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Actor
    The Actor is an abstract class which represents the actors in the game.
    AutomaticActor
    The AutomaticActor is an abstract class which represents the actors which can not controlled by the player.
    Car
    Horizontal moving cars in the game.
    End
    A End is a home of the Frog in the game.
    Frog
    A Frog is an object which is controlled by a player.
    Log
    Horizontal moving logs in the game.
    Turtle
    Horizontal moving turtles in the game.
    WetTurtle
    Horizontal moving wet turtles in the game.
